%N A091347 a(n) = 6*4^n - 12*3^n + 7*2^n - 1.
%H A091347 Bruce Nye, <a href="/A091347/b091347.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..1000</a>
%H A091347 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (10,-35,50,-24).
%F A091347 a(n) = Sum_{i=1..n} i!*i^3*Stirling2(n,i)*(-1)^(n-i).
%F A091347 From _Elmo R. Oliveira_, May 08 2026: (Start)
%F A091347 G.f.: x*(1 + 5*x) / ((1-x)*(1-2*x)*(1-3*x)*(1-4*x)).
%F A091347 E.g.f.: exp(x)*(6*exp(3*x) - 12*exp(2*x) + 7*exp(x) - 1).
%F A091347 a(n) = 10*a(n-1) - 35*a(n-2) + 50*a(n-3) - 24*a(n-4).
%F A091347 a(n) = A162723(n+1) - 1. (End)
%t A091347 Table[6*4^n - 12*3^n + 7*2^n - 1, {n, 0, 25}]
%o A091347 (PARI) a(n) = sum(i=1, n, i!*i^3*stirling(n, i, 2)*(-1)^(n-i)); \\ _Michel Marcus_, Oct 21 2022
